# Deepr - minimal setup. One API key is enough to start.
#
#   cp .env.example .env        (then paste a key below)
#   deepr doctor                (verifies your setup)
#   deepr budget set 5          (hard monthly spending ceiling, in dollars)
#   deepr research "your question"
#
# Every other setting has a sensible default. The full template with all
# providers and options (Azure, webhooks, cloud storage, tuning knobs) is
# in .env.example.full - copy sections from it into .env as you need them.

# Pick at least one provider key:
OPENAI_API_KEY=
# GEMINI_API_KEY=             https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey
# XAI_API_KEY=                https://console.x.ai/
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=          https://console.anthropic.com/settings/keys

# Optional: hard cost ceilings (also settable via `deepr budget set`)
# DEEPR_MAX_COST_PER_JOB=5
# DEEPR_MAX_COST_PER_DAY=10
# DEEPR_MAX_COST_PER_MONTH=50
